  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个健康科技系统的数据流图。核心模块是HIPAA合规的数据保险库，我暂时叫它HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault，还有患者记录系统HealthTech_PatientRecords。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，Vault和PatientRecords是两个独立节点。我注意到您提到了两次HIPAA_Vault，是同一个实体还是不同的？另外系统里还有分析模块吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是同一个实体，我口误了。另外还有实验室分析器HealthTech_LabAnalyzer和诊断引擎HealthTech_DiagnosticEngine。LabAnalyzer会把数据传给DiagnosticEngine做进一步处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在把LabAnalyzer指向DiagnosticEngine的连线加上。同时我也把HIPAA_Vault到DiagnosticEngine的审计链路画出来，这样合规检查就完整了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Audit"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，Audit到Define这条线很关键，用于审计追踪。不过患者记录和HIPAA_Vault之间应该是双向同步的关系，不是单向的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "双向同步，那就是Bail和Barg之间要画两条反向的箭头。我调整一下，让PatientRecords和HIPAA_Vault互相指向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还需要加上风险监控层。有Risk节点发出Signal，然后Signal再触发HIPAA_Vault的响应机制。另外Place节点会触发Press动作作为系统压力测试。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Risk指向Signal，Signal指向Barg，然后Place指向Press。Press是一个动作节点还是终点？图上看起来它没有后续了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Press是终点，表示压力测试的触发完成。不过我刚发现DiagnosticEngine也应该能直接访问HIPAA_Vault获取历史数据，这条线漏了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了Define到Barg的连线。现在整个流向是：LabAnalyzer→DiagnosticEngine→HIPAA_Vault，同时DiagnosticEngine也能反向查询Vault，对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，方向反了。DiagnosticEngine到HIPAA_Vault是查询关系，但HIPAA_Vault本身不应该主动推数据给DiagnosticEngine。让我重新理清：应该是Define→Barg，而不是双向。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Define",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "已修正，Define单向指向Barg。现在所有关系都对了：审计Vault监控诊断引擎，诊断引擎查询Vault，患者记录与Vault双向同步，风险信号触发Vault，LabAnalyzer驱动诊断流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Barg",
        "Bail",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Code"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
